lead_paragraph: Olympic sailing began an 11-day regatta on Monday with near perfect winds as competitors showed little fear of heading back into waters criticised for sewage-borne pathogens and floating garbage.

headline.print_headline: Sailing-Regatta Sets Sail on Dirty Water, Tricky Winds
